  "title": "Admin executive",
  "description": "<h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><p><ul><li>Manage daily office operations and administrative activities</li></ul></p><ul><li><p>Maintain records, files, and documentation (physical and digital)</p></li><li><p>Handle incoming calls, emails, and correspondence</p></li><li><p>Coordinate meetings, appointments, and schedules</p></li><li><p>Support HR activities such as attendance, leave records, and onboarding documentation</p></li><li><p>Assist in procurement of office supplies and vendor coordination</p></li><li><p>Prepare reports, presentations, and official documents</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with company policies and procedures<br /></p><p><strong>Preferred Skills</strong></p><p>-Knowledge of basic accounting or billing processes</p><p>-Familiarity with accounting software like Xero</p><p><p>-Problem-solving and decision-making skills</p></p></li></ul>",
